<h1>First Days</h1>

<p>First Days helps you to support volunteers through the recruitment process, from assessing your needs, right through to getting feedback on the volunteers first day.</p>

<p class="alert alert-info">Click on section one to begin. Once you have completed the activities of each section, return to this page and move on to the next.</p>

<br/>

<div><%= link "1. Answer questions to help us create a role description for the volunteer", to: role_description_path(@conn, :role_description_new) %></div>
<br/>
<div><%= link "2. Role Description template", to: role_description_path(@conn, :role_description_show) %></div>
<br/>
<div><%= link "3. Volunteer agreement", to: confirmation_agreement_path(@conn, :confirmation_agreement_show) %></div>
<br/>
<div><%= link "4. Answer questions to help us create a list of documents the volunteer needs to provide", to: document_checklist_path(@conn, :document_checklist_edit) %></div>
<br/>
<div><%= link "5. Document Checklist template", to: document_checklist_path(@conn, :document_checklist_show) %></div>
<br/>
<div><%= link "6. Answer questions to help us create an email informing the volunteer of everything they need to prepare for their first day", to: preparation_path(@conn, :preparation_edit) %></div>
<br/>
<div><%= link "7. First day preparation email template", to: preparation_path(@conn, :preparation_show) %></div>
<br/>
<div><%= link "8. Volunteer feedback email template", to: feedback_path(@conn, :feedback_show) %></div>
